Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# The Way She Flies 她的飛相
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.28,0:00:02.02,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}來，我們學了什麼\NNow, what have we learned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.39,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}很多的控制\NLots of control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:03.85,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}很好\NGood
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:05.19,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}大聲尖叫\NScreaming and hollering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.62,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}對，而最重要的是\NYes, and most importantly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:08.26,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}熱情\NPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:08.86,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}嘿\NRight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:11.56,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}那現在你知道歡呼的元素\NSo now that you know the elements of a good cheer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.53,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}來，聽一個\Nlet's, hear one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}一...二...三...\N1... 2... 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,上！\NGO!
Comment: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一道紅色\NFlash of red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神的她飛上天\Nthe spectral wonder takes flight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她很確定，她很堅定，她感覺很爽\Nand she's ready and she's steady and she's feelin' just right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她有熱情，有動力，有決心要贏\NShe got the passion, the drive, the tenacity to win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}而只要十秒她就能讓你頭昏眼花\Nand in 10 seconds flat she'll take your head for a spin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,天如火燒，彷彿漸漸變成一顆密桃\NSky is burnin' and it's turnin' to a tangerine peach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在海南島沙灘的太陽下山\Nlike a sun slowly settin' over Huntington Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她的肚子裡有顆火\NShe's got a fire in her belly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:55.46,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,嘿！\NYep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛裡有火\Nfire in her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:56.83,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,對！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,超音速的步伐在空中留下火跡\Nsupersonic strut leaves a fire in the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,越發亮，變成溫暖的金光\NBrighten up to a warm and golden glow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他充滿你的從腳到頭\Nlet it fill you all up from your head to your toe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讓那太陽閃在你頭\Nlet that sun shine down on ya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都叫大聲點\Neverypony scream louder
Comment: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,七彩在天空中\N7 colors in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看他飛過天空\NWatch her dash on by
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂被遮住\NThe heavens are covered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,被如此的景色\Nwith so many wonders
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛她的飛相\NI love the way she flies
