Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有片青青草地\NWe got the green green grass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還有翡翠綠樹\Nand the emerald trees
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還有平原上的兔子、鳥兒，跟蜜蜂\Nand the meadows with the bunnies and the birds and the bees
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而我，真希望能從她的角度看看\Nand I wish I could see it from her point of view
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,直接從那，一大片藍天的中間\Nstraight up there in the middle of the big ol' blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要是可以我一定還會帶你去\Nand I would if I could and I would take you too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,飛過永恆森林，到坎特拉城去\Nover the Everfree Forest to a Canterlot view
